text: Daniel Ytterbom (born 18 September 1976) is a Swedish professional footballer, currently player as a forward for Sjötulls BK. Ytterbom began his career with Gefle IF, turning professional in 1993, having played for their Under-19 side. He had a trial with Torquay United in October 1999, but returned to Gefle and remained there until joining Sjötulls BK in January 2007. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish footballers Category:Gefle IF players Category:Association football forwards
